{"tid":1985582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外電指中共擬以近日低價購入3000萬噸農產品 以履行中美貿易協議","createTime":"2020-04-23T08:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T08:48:02.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e66905b28926ff403b3babbb196dd944aff4c090","tid":1985582,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"外電指中國擬購逾3000萬噸農產品大部分美國進口<br />\n23.04.2020 16:18<br />\n<br />\n外電引述消息指，中國準備購買超過3000萬噸農產品，以補充國家儲備，當中大部分由美國進口，以履行中美首階段貿易協議中，中方購買更多美國農產品的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指，近日商品價格相當低，現在正是增加儲備的大好時機，中國打算購買大約1000萬噸大豆、2000萬噸玉米、100萬噸棉花，以防疫情造成供應鏈中斷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282840&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282840%26csid%3D261_367&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=53266def\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282840&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"b481f74897e5aaeda46f9bfa2608c2d4ba6ec992","tid":1985582,"uid":177590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏"},{"pid":"bf1212d3c47f94838c9a70b4cb84bd9ca6d61293","tid":1985582,"uid":280136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"買曬美國貨，美國人冇得食就要死<br />\n我黨又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}